short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Remove the fuss of having to click on every eval button and write an evaluation when you can do it with a single click.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Tired of filling AISIS Eval Forms? This extension will help you evaluate 10x faster! (Only fills one evaluation form at a time, but still, it's faster)

How to use:
1) Pin the extension

2) Open the extension on the aisis evaluation page. 

3) Select and input the proper values

4) Click auto fill form!


DISCLAIMER:
We do not collect any data or survey answers from you, everything is kept in your local browser. We will not see any of your evaluations.
